<NEW>

Cryotek nodded, "Of course." he said, a small smile tugging at his
lips as he did so. "I will have Strika and her soldiers escort you and
your men to the edge of the city to see that you have gotten on your
way safely." Cryotek gestured at the female soldiers that had escorted
them through the halls.

One of the soldiers stepped foward and glanced at Cryotek, her
distaste for this mission evident on her face. A firm nod from Cryotek
had her turning back to Hydras.

"Follow me." she said shortly to Hydras and began walking towards the
door. "I will lead you out . . . safely." Behind Hydras several of the
other female soldiers came up, lending a certain emphasis to her
command.

Cryotek folded his arms across his chest as he watched, a certain
humor in his optics.
